  "original_title": "\u0db8\u0db1\u0dca\u0db1\u0dcf\u0dbb\u0db8 \u0db0\u0dd3\u0dc0\u0dbb \u0dc0\u0dcf\u0da9\u0dd2\u0dba\u0d9a\u0da7 \u0d9c\u0dd2\u0db1\u0dd2 \u0dad\u0dd0\u0db6\u0dd3\u0db8\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dca \u0d9a\u0ddd\u0da7\u0dd2\u0dba\u0d9a \u0db4\u0dcf\u0da9\u0dd4\u0dc0\u0d9a\u0dca",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "A loss of one crore due to the burning of a fishing village in Mannar",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "According to the Pesalai Police, the fishermen have suffered a loss of nearly one crore rupees due to a group of people setting fire to a fishing village in the Pesalai area of \u200b\u200bMannar last night (16th).",
        "Fishermen say that a group of people who suddenly came to the fishing lodge in Pesalai set it on fire and ran away.",
        "Also, 500 kilos of prawns, 800 kilos of prawns, over 100 kilos of fish and many nets caught by the fishermen have been completely destroyed by the fire.",
        "Before setting fire to the fishermen's wadis, there was a conflict between two groups of fishermen in the Pesalai area and it is also reported that the fishermen's wadis have been set on fire while a complaint is being investigated by the Pesalai Police.",
        "After the related fire, the affected fishermen have also submitted a complaint to the Mannar Senior Superintendent of Police and the Pesalai Police and the Mannar Police have started a comprehensive investigation to find the persons involved in the fire."
      ],
